{"tid":1086782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東北人要求廣東老人院退押金 院方指聽不懂普通話收線","createTime":"2019-04-01T03:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T04:44:48.000Z","uid":144372,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7036f311f1cd92e7dff5529c2b0caca55ec0351d","tid":1086782,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cssqt.com/xw/gn/sh/256669.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cssqt.com%2Fxw%2Fgn%2Fsh%2F256669.shtml&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6jw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=ba3a6e14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cssqt.com/xw/gn/sh/256669.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n傅先生是東北人，來清遠工作一年，因為工​​作繁忙無暇照顧父親。去年11月，傅先生將父親送進了東城頤養院。<br />\n<br />\n在這之前，傅先生在網上了解過這家養老院，評價是很不錯的，來到實地看過養老院的環境也挺滿意，在得到了父親的同意後，就為他辦理了入住手續。<br />\n<br />\n本想讓父親安享晚年，可在4月底，傅先生的父親在養老院意外摔倒，幾天后突然離世。料理完父親的後事後，傅先生向頤養院要求退回入院押金，由於傅先生丟失了這張押金條， 醫院方面要求一定要有押金條才能退還押金，因此拒絕了退款。<br />\n<br />\n傅先生為父親辦理的是一級特殊護理，但父親摔倒後竟然幾天就突然離世，他認為，是養老院的醫療水平太低，而且他了解到這裡的醫生是沒有職業資格證的。<br />\n<br />\n具體情況到底是怎麼回事呢？記者嘗試採訪該養老機構負責人，但是院方卻以<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽不懂普通話</span></ins></strong>掛斷了電話&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n傅先生則說他見過幾次院長，因為是外地人不會粵語，所以跟院長的交流都是用普通話，<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">院長說她不懂普通話那是不可能的。</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"36669f0427ed25b18e32a6d07c170ce65c3df952","tid":1086782,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee6710f9f19917daf1486ab5a625eb82d6ca88a","tid":1086782,"uid":237562,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港都應該行呢套啦"},{"pid":"2d156c296464941d9d6caf718725eb0c8a1ba584","tid":1086782,"uid":52031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d0ceb9b4a1a8c45113ef61d08d9ceb3a69b84e","tid":1086782,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"蝗 -1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75517570d585addb820375c8b626ad70c9ff1f0d","tid":1086782,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"傅先生為父親辦理的是一級特殊護理，但父親摔倒後竟然幾天就突然離世<br />\n<br />\n正宗仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}